    <p>{`Terraform uses provider plugins to generate resources for different infrastructure components. Plugins allow terraform capabilities to be extended and new resource classes to be provisioned. The providers and plugins maintained by Hashicorp, the creator of Terraform, reside in a set of repositories in the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`terraform-providers`}</inlineCode>{` organization in Github. Third party providers and plugins can also be housed in other Github repositories.`}</p>
